a>&nbsp;Technische Universit&auml;t Berlin</p><h3>英德双语项目</h3><p>普通硕士课程（Internationale konsekutive Masterstudieng&auml;nge）</p><ul>	<li>环境规划（Umweltplanung）硕士（Environmental Planning (Umweltplanung), M.Sc.）</li>	<li>环境政策与规划硕士 （Environmental Policy and Planning, M.A.）</li>	<li>科学计算硕士（Scientific Computing, M.Sc.）</li>	<li>信息系统管理硕士（Information Systems Management, M.Sc.）*(1)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=BraKR4YIw0DYWaFJdddddc7BKw6qzebtyXyXN4nX71qy0tKiwO-iYOo0J5-LwQIdTO-iY5zhwF-0hFGJh5UdfOGHJLUMhLJH5mtHjFXRrLU6rmt5aLAuTDU5r2Z5j7tyTmt1PGXHPkXH1eXSPGZ5rmtuJDU50LUuM2m' target='_blank'>International Programs</a>&nbsp;Technische Universit&auml;t Berlin</p></div>
					
